<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NodeJS Machine Test</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }
        
        body {
            background-color: #f5f7fa;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 90%;
        }
        
        h1 {
            color: #4361ee;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }
        
        p {
            color: #6c757d;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        
        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .nav-links a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background: #4361ee;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .nav-links a:hover {
            background: #3a56d4;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }
        
        .features {
            text-align: left;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        
        .features h2 {
            color: #4361ee;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .features ul {
            list-style-type: none;
        }
        
        .features li {
            padding: 8px 0;
            color: #6c757d;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .features li:before {
            content: "âœ“";
            color: #4361ee;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .nav-links {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 10px;
            }
            
            .nav-links a {
                width: 100%;
                text-align: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>NodeJS Machine Test Application</h1>
        <p>Manage your categories and products with ease</p>
        
       
        
        <div class="features">
            <h2>Application Features</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Full CRUD operations for categories</li>
                <li>Full CRUD operations for products</li>
                <li>Server-side pagination for products</li>
                <li>MySQL database integration</li>
                <li>Responsive design for all devices</li>
                
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>